{"tid":1737940,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"被帶風向的黎明行動","createTime":"2019-11-19T05:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T09:59:51.000Z","uid":267959,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"13ab398d24c5868262935ace476b6cb201e09fd7","tid":1737940,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:51:11.000Z","msg":"三罷實行多日，究竟有冇人發現沒咩收穫，成日話捉住政府春袋。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">連讀書都可以網上授課</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">BUSINESS D 科技絕對比學校高</span></span></strong><br />\n我公司沒開3日，但個個同事開會的開會、交貨的交貨<br />\n你哋唔信可以揾IT 狗問下<br />\n三罷只會影響到基層，而佢哋本身就對抗爭沒感，只為生活，宜家當然恨抗爭者更多<br />\n最重要係佢哋聲音政府聽過就算，佢哋又唔係坐係中環D老細，政府會有壓力?<br />\n仲有經過POLYU件事，封路封到成了困獸鬥<br />\n戰術上懇請各位仔細檢討，唔好再一失足成千古恨<br />\n這次為營救POLYU各方都出盡九牛二虎之力，連求救建制派都做埋了<br />\n<br />\n一定有人鬧我又有咩好建議<br />\n宜家係咩世代呀，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">科技</span></span></strong>決定一切<br />\n一個DDOS攻擊，可以立刻讓政府收皮<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位condemn我，但唔該理性思考完再來condemn"},{"pid":"36c34dadc2ff686ba9aedd2396ead5490d04143c","tid":1737940,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:52:17.000Z","msg":"20"},{"pid":"01ddb8ed32ffc8d17765e06e9b53d8a734a739db","tid":1737940,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:52:28.000Z","msg":"19"},{"pid":"94850e7ab4135da2dbb5ed128b4f3dc5dd698fab","tid":1737940,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:52:38.000Z","msg":"18"},{"pid":"bebf404b64203732b123d900fc06f5610e545bef","tid":1737940,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:52:49.000Z","msg":"17"},{"pid":"be06f24e3f9d71d802ed5bd70ee7b49f15ce7475","tid":1737940,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:52:59.000Z","msg":"16"},{"pid":"fae5609681fa03590f109d370252c88f3adefbb2"